ng and switched to a random decision-making strategy. Together, these findings exemplify both the bats' decision-making plasticity as well as its natural limitations.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Naamani, Goni", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Shahar, Nitzan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ger, Yoav", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Yovel, Yossi", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/077c834e4ecefc683129c40b6f4997ce", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/590e6c5d16b1085beac7cdc055d75dca0e2cb6a299297eebf629b0075deee7a5", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/W6GGTPH3", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/W6GGTPH3", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/a7a9ef34a8f5c61e5604ecd8e3bd0a12!/b7488-9955", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "278", "title": "BMC Biology", "volume": "21"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/077c834e4ecefc683129c40b6f4997ce"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:W6GGTPH3"}, {"identifier": "10.1186/s12915-023-01774-0"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "re